OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA wet start but rain clearing
OL,6,Feast through the morning, followed by
OL,7,Fbrighter spells and some showers. The
OL,8,Fshowers tending to be focussed towards
OL,9,Fthe northwest, and locally heavy here.
OL,10,FHowever, elsewhere largely dry and
OL,11,Fbright. Breezy but feeling milder.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny showers easing overnight,
OL,14,Fwith most areas becoming largely dry
OL,15,Fby dawn. A brisk breeze continuing
OL,16,Fovernight, with temperatures remaining
OL,17,Fon the mild side.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
